More Ultra HD content, More Ultra HD channels with DISH
DISH technology makes it easier for you to enjoy more 4K TV programming on your Ultra HD TV. From OnDemand movies, shows and events to Netflix programming and more, DISH offers a varied selection of UHD content. Take a look at how DISH’s state-of-the-art 4K receivers let you tune into available 4K channels, movies and shows.
Learn More






How to Watch 4K TV
Whether you call it 4K, Ultra HD, or Ultra High-Def, today’s high-resolution TV is easy to watch with DISH. Here’s all you need to start watching 4K TV:

Your 4K Ultra HD TV
Our Hopper 3 DVR
A package with DISH
Netflix 4K Programming for additional UHD content (additional service subscriptions may apply)







Hopper 3
The Hopper 3 DVR receiver is your gateway to great UHD content. With the Hopper 3, you're ready to start watching the most popular 4K programming available. Use the Hopper 3’s sleek User Interface to access 4K Netflix content and OnDemand Ultra HD movies and shows. And as more networks begin airing 4K shows, games, and movies, you’ll be ready to tune in with the Hopper 3.
Learn More





4K Joey
If you have multiple 4K TVs in your home or if you’re considering adding more in the future, this whole-home technology is for you. With the 4K Joey, you can watch Ultra HD programming on any 4K TV in your home. Our Joey 4K receivers connect with your Hopper 3 to let you watch 4K TV in any room in your home where you have an Ultra HD TV.
Learn More







