The award-winning Hopper changes the game with its unique ability to instantly skip commercials in certain programs in recorded primetime TV on ABC, CBS, FOX and NBC. Record up to 6 live channels at once and store 500 hours of HD recordings. Access apps like Pandora, Game Finder, Weather and more. Read more



The highly-awarded Hopper 2 gives you the freedom to enjoy 100% of your live channels and DVR recordings, as well as thousands of OnDemand titles even when you're away from home. Record up to 6 live channels at once and store 500 hours of HD recordings. Turn every TV in your home into a smart TV with access to  apps like Netflix and Pandora. With this new on-screen experience your TV has never looked so good. Read more



"The most ludicrously powerful"  cable box ever  Wired magazine (Jan 2016).
With the ability to record 16 programs at once there shouldn't be any issue watching and recording everything you want in your home. Only the Hopper gives you the freedom to enjoy 100% of your live TV and DVR recordings at home AND on the go. Store 500 hours of HD recordings and turn every TV in your home into a smart TV with access to apps like Netflix and Pandora. With this new on-screen experience your TV has never looked so good. Read more

 

Secondary
Based on how many TVs you have, we recommend an additional Hopper 2 to power and connect even more entertainment spaces in your home. This additional Hopper gives you the power to record 3 additional programs - up to 9 channels at once with the same features as your first TV. You may want to expect more guests with this loaded entertainment set-up. Read more

 

Secondary
Based on how many TVs you have, we recommend an additional Hopper to power and connect even more entertainment spaces in your home. This additional Hopper gives you the power to record 3 additional programs - up to 9 channels at once with the same features as your first TV. You may want to expect more guests with this loaded entertainment set-up. Read more



For additional TVs in your home the Hopper's smaller but powerful complementary receiver, Joey is recommended. A Joey connects other TVs in the home with a Hopper to create a whole-home entertainment experience where you can pause or record on any TV and access it from another TV. Joeys have all the same great benefits of the Hopper and can be wired or wireless; plus they are compact enough to tuck behind the TV or inside a cabinet with ease. Read more



Based on how many TVs you have, we recommend additional TVs be supported by the Super Joey. A Super Joey allows you to connect even more TVs together just like a Joey, but with the power to record 2 additional programs you'll be able to watch and record a total of 8 at once. With the whole Hopper family at your disposal you're sure to have one of the best viewing and recording experiences available today. Read more



A Wally  uses our most modern and up-to-date on-screen experience. It supports one independent viewing HDTV with access to apps like Netflix, Pandora, Game Finder and more. Read more

 

Secondary
Wally receivers are great for additional TVs as well. You'll enjoy the same modern on-screen experience as your first TV with all of the same features as your first TV including HD and access to apps. Read more


HD Duo DVR
HD Duo DVR receivers support 2 TVs, with the ability to watch and record in HD on one TV and in SD (standard definition) on the other. Watch a pre-recorded show while recording two separate shows at the same time. Pause, rewind and record live TV with ease. Read more





