WELCOME TO DISH
If you’ve been referred by a friend to DISH, sign up now and get your pick of great rewards like a FREE Echo Dot, 12 FREE Pay-per-view movies, or $50 in bill credits*!


Step 1: Enter your friend’s referral code. 
 Step 2: Select a DISH TV package and activate your service. 
Step 3: Choose a reward. Your friend picks one too! 













Redeem Now


Already a DISH customer? Head over to www.myDISH.com/refer to request a Referral Code today and begin referring your friends! $5/mo. credit for 10 months.*

 Important TermsOffer ends 10/18/17. New service must be installed by 10/18/17. Rewards must be redeemed online within 60 days of new activation and are subject to change. Maximum of 10 referrals per calendar year. New or qualified former DISH customers must provide a valid, original certificate number at time of order for service, prior to installation and activation. Certificate is nonrefundable, not redeemable for cash, nontransferable and may not be combined with other Reward offers. Certificate(s) may be deactivated and referral eligibility may be revoked. Other restrictions apply. All prices, fees, packages, charges, features, functionality, and programming subject to change without notice. Free Echo Dot provided by DISH. Amazon is not a sponsor of this promotion. Requires internet-connected Hopper® or Wally™ and Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, or Amazon Tap. Amazon, Alexa, Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap, and all related logos are trademarks of Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates. Visit mydish.com/refer for full details. © 2017 DISH Network L.L.C. All rights reserved. 

