Hopper 3  – The World’s Most Powerful DVR
Change channels, pause, rewind, fast-forward, search, and more with just the sound of your voice. But that’s not all: The Hopper 3 can also record twice as many shows at once as any other provider’s DVR, and only DISH lets you take 100% of the live and recorded TV you get at home, anywhere, on any device.
Learn More
Watching live and recorded TV anywhere requires DISH Anywhere app, an internet-connected, Sling-enabled DVR, and compatible mobile device.









