Watch and record up to 16 shows at once
View 4 HD channels at once on split screen
Built-in 4k Ultra HD 
Faster Navigation
New user interface and faster navigation

Also includes all the benefits of the Hopper 2 - learn more.





HOPPER 2 SMART DVR

Integrated apps: Netflix, Pandora, Vevo, and Youtube
Access to 100% of your live and recorded content on the go

Also includes all the benefits of the Hopper 1 - learn more.





HOPPPER SMART DVR

Watch and record up to 6 shows at once
Store 500+ hours of HD (2TB)
Skip commercials with one click on all PrimeTime Anytime recordings
1,000+ On Demand programs
Remote Control Locator
